      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KOORINGA KATE (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.99) in a NG at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. Looks the one to beat on her best form. BARLEY CHARLIE (1) made light work of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (20.15) at Grafton over 350m. Expected to be in the finish again. BULL MUNDY (8) missed the frame latest (20.57) when fourth over 350m at Grafton in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. LITTLE GIRL GONE (3) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
